ArcGIS,is,a,geospatial,solution,for,developing,mapping,and,location,applications,The,Esri,ArcGIS,GeoEnrichment,Service,API,provides,access,to,location,specific,facts,and,data,The,API,is,useful,to,retrieving,descriptive,profiles,of,specific,locations,and,neighboring,areas,including,people,businesses,geographic,contexts,and,geographic,boundaries,Users,can,access,the,demographic,breakdown,of,a,chosen,location,by,simply,sending,a,point,or,polygon,to,the,ArcGIS,GeoEnrichment,Service,API